.Dd August 1, 1996
.Dt LOGIN_LCHPASS 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm login_lchpass
.Nd change local password authentication type
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm login_lchpass
.Op Fl s Ar service
.Ar user
.Op Ar class
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Pp
The
.Nm
utility is typically called from
.Xr login 8 .
It is functionally the same as calling the program:
.Dq passwd -l Ar user .
.Pp
Only the
.Li login
service is supported.
See
.Xr login.conf 5 .
The
.Ar class
argument is not used.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr passwd 1 ,
.Xr login.conf 5 ,
.Xr login 8
